<p>must be solved by a numerical method, such as</p>

<ul>
 <li> Newton's method</li>
 <li> The Bisection method</li>
 <li> Fixed-point (Picard) iteration by rewriting \( f(x)=x - g(x) \)</li>
 <li> The Secant method</li>
</ul>
